 ],
 "name": "RPlog_The_Suicide_Attempt",
 "title": "The Suicide Attempt",
 "summary": "Aboard the freighter Black Dragon, the despondent Wookiee Chewbacca brings the Jedi Jessalyn Valios to translate a tense confrontation with the captive CSA Colonel Roark -- called Xegid -- revealing that Dillon and the Prex have betrayed them both. Through Jessalyn's careful translation, Chewbacca and Roark trade bitter philosophy about honor, selfishness, and profit, Chewbacca insisting his loyalty to Han Solo is the same fierce devotion Roark would show his own daughter. Roark, embittered and now free to go, is told he will be treated as a guest, but the wounding exchange ends with him walking out -- only for a guard to report he has done something terrible in the engine room. Chewbacca and Jessalyn rush to find Roark wedged into the machinery, having electrocuted himself in a suicide attempt. Chewbacca cuts the power and Jessalyn drags his limp, smoking body free; finding a pulse but no breathing, she revives him with rescue breaths until he gasps on his own. Chewbacca carries the barely living, badly burned Roark toward the medbay as the ship docks with the NRV Hyperon, and a frantic Jessalyn races ahead to beg Coreen and Kuxli for a medical team."
}